culiar that way.\n\n- Cassandra Clare, Clockwork Angel\n|\nIf your heart is pure, you block any harm.\n\n- Lailah\n|\nTo an unmoored, middle-aged man like myself, it was heart-breaking. That’s all right. I like to have my heart broken.\n\n- Kurt\n|\nIf I preached unity, I must act like a unifier, even at the risk of perhaps alienating some of my own colleagues.\n\n- Nelson\n|\nLook to the past with wisdom, and look to the future with courage.\n\n- Stacey\n|\nKnow that blank pages feel the urge of the ink as much as tears paint a different pain, changes\n\n- Goitsemang\n|\nA long apprenticeship is the most logical way to success. The only alternative is overnight stardom, but I can't give you a formula for that.\n\n- Chet\n|\nFor the girl without words, there is laughter for what is light, gesture for want, and tears for all that is dark. There is not much more. Names are nothing but extravagance.\n\n- Lois-Ann Yamanaka, Blu's Hanging\n|\nIn these last days, what the world really needs is courageous parenting from mothers and fathers who are not afraid to speak up and take a stand.\n\n- Larry\n|\nThe good thing about being numb is that no one can hurt you, but the bad thing about being numb is that no one can love you.\n\n- Kaiylah Muhammad, The Starving Psyche\n|\nA warrior doesn’t worry. He or she evaluates the situation, investigates the source, calculates the risks and benefits, formulates a plan then puts it into action.\n\n- Shannon\n|\nTo find wealth, we may not need to mine for treasure if we learn how to mine between our ears.\n\n- Debasish\n|\nNo matter how small you start, always dream and think BIG. If you start with small thoughts then you will stay with small thoughts.\n\n- Stephen Richards, Six Figure Success: Time To Think Big - You Can Do It\n|\nIf someone doesn't care to accept you, respect you, believe in you, don't hesitate to move on and let them go. There are many who love and appreciate you just the way you are.\n\n- Amaka Imani Nkosazana, Swee